make clean
make veryclean

!!!!!!!!!! how to run !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
(1) quantum chemistry calculations with G09
(2) ./normal_mode_g09.sh name_of_G09.log 
(3) ./vsfg vsfg.in 




